Axaṭer ur nețțuɣal a nsel i ṣṣut n wid yekkaten snitra d wid i gcennun akk-d wid yekkaten ajewwaq d lbuq. Ur d-yețɣimi deg-em ṣṣaneɛ, ur nețțɣal a nsel i iɣuṛaf n tessirt.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ. Akka ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti , ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Ula d kečč a gma Sizugus unṣiḥ, ḍelbeɣ-ak a tent-tɛiwneḍ nutenti i ḥurben yid-i ɣef ddemma n lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, akk-d Klimun d imdukkal-iw nniḍen di leqdic iwumi uran yismawen nsen di tektabt n tudert.
Deg yiwet n tama reggmen-t, kksen fell-awen sser, si tama nniḍen tbeddem ɣer wid iwumi yedṛa wayagi.
